Projection's half-size when in orthographic mode.

This is half of the vertical size of the projection volume. Horizontal projection
size varies depending on ::ref::aspectRatio.
Orthographic size is ignored when projection is not orthographic (see ::ref::orthographic).
SA: [[wiki:class-Projector|projector component]].
CONVERTEXAMPLE
BEGIN EX

	function Start() {
		var proj : Projector = GetComponent(Projector);
		proj.orthographic = true;
		proj.orthographicSize = 2.0;
	}
END EX